      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, boundary conditions, and operating regime are representative of COU geometry and operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry assessed in the COU. Operating points span the full clinical flow-speed envelope. Boundary conditions (inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure) were matched to bench test conditions within measurement uncertainty."
    },
    {
